;</rt></ruby>「<ruby>得<rt>&thinsp;ㄉ丨ㆵ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>通<rt>&thinsp;ㄊㄤ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>」的縮音字)<ruby>解<rt>&thinsp;ㄍㄞˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>決<rt>&thinsp;ㄍㄨㄚㆵ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>問<rt>&thinsp;ㆠㄨㄣ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>題<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㆤˊ/ㄉㄨㆤˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。⑥助商量語氣。 例：叫他畫個押～！(台)<ruby>抑<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄚㆷ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>無<rt>&thinsp;ㆠㄜˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>叫<rt>&thinsp;ㄍ丨ㄜ˪&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>伊<rt>&thinsp;丨&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>畫<rt>&thinsp;ㄨㆤ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>一<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㆵ̇&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>個<rt>&thinsp;ㆤˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>花<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㄨㆤ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>押<rt>&thinsp;ㄚㆷ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(/<ruby>押<rt>&thinsp;ㄚㆷ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>花<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㄨㆤ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>押<rt>&thinsp;ㄚㆷ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>)<ruby>喏<rt>&thinsp;ㄋㆦㆷ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(/<ruby>嗬<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㆧㆷ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>)。類語：<ruby>唄<rt>&thinsp;ㄅㄟ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。<ruby>㗑<rt>&thinsp;ㄅㄞ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。<ruby>啵<rt>&thinsp;ㄅㄛ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。

