        dd  <ruby>用<rt>&thinsp;丨ㆲ˫/丨ㄥ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>耙<rt>&thinsp;ㄅㆤ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>仔<rt>&thinsp;˙ㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>將<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㆲ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>地<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㄨㆤ˫/ㄉㆤ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>面<rt>&thinsp;ㆠ丨ㄣ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>拖<rt>&thinsp;ㄊㄨㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>平<rt>&thinsp;ㄅㆳˊ/ㄅㆥˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>、<ruby>將<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㆲ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>柴<rt>&thinsp;ㄘㄚˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>草<rt>&thinsp;ㄘㄠˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>耙<rt>&thinsp;ㄅㆤˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>倚<rt>&thinsp;ㄨㄚˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>或<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄚㆷ̇&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>是<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>攤<rt>&thinsp;ㄊㄨㆩˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>開<rt>&thinsp;ㄎㄨ丨&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。
        dd
